// Global Design System Guide for Cursor AI
// This file defines the styling and layout rules for UI generation

// ✅ Libraries to use
// - Use shadcn/ui components for all buttons, inputs, cards, tabs, modals, etc.
// - Use Tailwind CSS utility classes for spacing, layout, and visual styling.
// - Use lucide-react icons for any iconography (e.g., `import { User, Settings } from "lucide-react"`)

// ✅ Layout Guidelines
// - Use responsive design with `flex`, `grid`, and `container` Tailwind utilities
// - All layouts should have generous padding (e.g., `p-4`, `p-6`) and spacing (`gap-4` or more)
// - Prefer `max-w-7xl mx-auto` for main page content wrappers

// ✅ Component Style Rules
// 1. Cards
//    - Use `Card`, `CardHeader`, `CardContent` from shadcn
//    - Apply `rounded-2xl`, `shadow-md`, `border`, `p-4`

// 2. Buttons
//    - Always use shadcn `Button`
//    - Include an icon from lucide-react on important action buttons
//    - Add hover/transition effects: `transition-all hover:scale-[1.02]`

// 3. Forms & Inputs
//    - Use `Label`, `Input`, `Textarea`, `Select` from shadcn
//    - Apply consistent spacing: `mb-4`, `space-y-2` within forms

// 4. Navigation
//    - Use vertical sidebar on left with icons + text
//    - Use `flex flex-col gap-4` for sidebar items
//    - Active items should have `bg-muted text-primary font-semibold`

// 5. Tables
//    - Wrap tables in a `Card`
//    - Use zebra striping: `odd:bg-muted` rows
//    - Add a sticky header if needed

// ✅ Typography
// - Use Tailwind’s `text-lg`, `text-xl`, `font-semibold`, `text-muted-foreground`
// - Section headings should use `text-xl font-bold mb-2`
// - Avoid excessive font sizes; balance weight and clarity

// ✅ Animation & Transitions
// - Add smooth transitions: `transition-all duration-200`
// - Use hover/focus states on interactive elements

// ✅ Colors
// - Use Tailwind color tokens and variants (e.g., `text-primary`, `bg-muted`, `border-muted`)
// - Avoid hardcoded hex colors

// ✅ Icons
// - Use lucide-react icons with Tailwind sizing (`w-5 h-5`) and spacing (`mr-2`)
// - Icons should complement text, not replace it

// ✅ Accessibility
// - All forms should have associated `Label`s
// - Use `aria-label` or `sr-only` where needed for screen readers
